  "translations": {
    "en": "He said: Abu Ghalib Ahmad ibn Muhammad al-Zurari, may Allah have mercy on him, reported to me from my uncle Abul Hasan Ali ibn Sulaiman ibn al-Jahm, from Abu Abdillah Muhammad ibn Khalid al-Tayalisi, from al-Ala' ibn Razin, from Muhammad ibn Muslim al-Thaqafi, who said: I asked Abu Ja'far Muhammad ibn Ali, peace be upon them both,",
